# TODO: add real keycheck-x86_64 binary

Binary artifacts are intentionally excluded from this patch context.

When binary support is available, build and add:
  x86_64-linux-gnu-gcc -O2 -static -o bin/keycheck/keycheck-x86_64 tools/keycheck.c
  chmod 755 bin/keycheck/keycheck-x86_64

Installer compatibility for x86_64 is already implemented in
bin/installer_config.sh via name/path probing and getevent fallback.
